<item>
            <title>[LU-119] Merge goof on master?</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-119</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like there was a goof in commit ab13b69b63ca19d7fe68b8ba6afd2cb4723db78c on master.  That patch reintroduces lines that were explicitly removed in commit 62345145fa7cae1846f96078bac43ddf58cea640.  I think that reintroduction was accidental, and needs to be corrected.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If it WASN&apos;T accidental, then it absolutely requires an explanation in the commit message.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
